12
00:00:30,060 --> 00:00:31,740
they will be different.

13
00:00:31,740 --> 00:00:34,790
But we can tell you more about the coverup.

14
00:00:34,790 --> 00:00:37,250
Remember those eight people who were detained
by police

15
00:00:37,250 --> 00:00:41,200
for “spreading rumors” about the coronavirus
back in December?

16
00:00:41,200 --> 00:00:44,310
It turns out, they were all doctors!

17
00:00:44,310 --> 00:00:47,310
The Beijing Youth Daily interviewed the original
doctor

18
00:00:47,310 --> 00:00:49,480
who spread the so-called rumor.

19
00:00:49,480 --> 00:00:50,881
It turns out, the doctor

20
00:00:50,881 --> 00:00:55,070
“had warned a WeChat group of former medical
school classmates

21
00:00:55,070 --> 00:00:57,850
about seven patients from a local wet market”

22
00:00:57,850 --> 00:01:02,720
who were exhibiting symptoms that he initially
thought was SARS.

23
00:01:02,720 --> 00:01:05,940
After screenshots from the private group leaked
on social media,

24
00:01:05,940 --> 00:01:08,560
“The doctor was summoned to a police station

25
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:10,750
and forced to confess his error

26
00:01:10,750 --> 00:01:13,000
and pledge not to repeat it.”

27
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:16,070
So were the other doctors in the group chat,
apparently.

28
00:01:16,070 --> 00:01:17,540
According to the Beijing Youth Daily,

29
00:01:17,540 --> 00:01:20,700
the doctor is now himself in an isolation
ward

30
00:01:20,700 --> 00:01:23,600
after he fell ill while treating patients.

31
00:01:23,600 --> 00:01:25,840
As you can imagine,

32
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:28,870
this news has contributed to the ongoing backlash

33
00:01:28,870 --> 00:01:33,299
against Chinese officials for covering up
news about the virus.

34
00:01:33,299 --> 00:01:34,870
People are so unhappy,

35
00:01:34,870 --> 00:01:39,049
that even the Supreme People’s Court has
published an article

36
00:01:39,049 --> 00:01:42,619
about how that the police were wrong for detaining
the doctor.

37
00:01:42,619 --> 00:01:44,340
The good news is, the Chinese Communist Party

38
00:01:44,340 --> 00:01:46,830
has obviously learned their lesson about the
need

39
00:01:46,830 --> 00:01:50,080
for greater openness in this time of crisis.

40
00:01:50,080 --> 00:01:53,840
Which is why the Party has ordered the article
about the doctor

41
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:55,880
be deleted from the internet.

42
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:57,380
Nothing to see here, folks.

43
00:01:57,380 --> 00:02:02,840
Ok, so maybe propaganda can’t defeat the
new coronavirus.

44
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:04,760
But you know what can?

45
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:06,040
Drones.

46
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:08,640
Specifically, drones that yell at you.

47
00:02:08,640 --> 00:02:11,920
Yes, auntie, this is the drone speaking to
you.

48
00:02:11,920 --> 00:02:15,060
You shouldn’t walk about without wearing
a mask.

49
00:02:15,060 --> 00:02:20,840
Yes, you’d better go back home and don’t
forget to wash your hands.

50
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:24,420
You see we’ve been telling people to stay
at home but you still wander outside.

51
00:02:24,460 --> 00:02:26,080
Now a drone is watching you.

52
00:02:26,090 --> 00:02:28,540
My favorite state-run media, The Global Times,

53
00:02:28,540 --> 00:02:32,669
published this compilation of drones in China
policing people

54
00:02:32,669 --> 00:02:34,749
and telling them to wear masks,

55
00:02:34,749 --> 00:02:36,360
or go back home.

56
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:38,829
Clearly, the best way to keep people healthy

57
00:02:38,829 --> 00:02:40,859
is to scare the bejeezus out of them,

58
00:02:40,860 --> 00:02:44,220
and then post that footage on China’s version
of TikTok.

59
00:02:44,220 --> 00:02:47,340
Hey kid! We are in unusual times!

60
00:02:47,340 --> 00:02:48,680
Don’t stroll around outside!

61
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:50,200
You don’t even wear a mask.

62
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:52,680
Hurry up and go back home!

63
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:55,600
The coronavirus is very serious...

64
00:02:57,540 --> 00:02:59,760
Run!! Don’t come outside.

65
00:02:59,760 --> 00:03:03,420
Staying home is contributing to society.

66
00:03:03,420 --> 00:03:06,319
That little girl just got yelled at by a drone.

67
00:03:06,319 --> 00:03:08,939
She’s never leaving her house again.

68
00:03:08,939 --> 00:03:11,079
In non coronavirus news,

69
00:03:11,079 --> 00:03:13,719
US Secretary of State Mike Pompeo

70
00:03:13,719 --> 00:03:15,779
had some pretty harsh words for China.

71
00:03:15,779 --> 00:03:20,459
“The Chinese Communist Party presents the
central threat of our times.”

72
00:03:20,459 --> 00:03:21,459
Central threat?

73
00:03:21,459 --> 00:03:24,159
Personally, I feel like it’s that second
helping of pancakes.

74
00:03:24,159 --> 00:03:25,739
Sure, it tastes great.

75
00:03:25,739 --> 00:03:28,379
But don’t expect your day to be productive
anymore.

76
00:03:28,379 --> 00:03:31,189
And too much of it will probably give you
a heart attack.

77
00:03:31,189 --> 00:03:35,449
