Chinese Communist Party.

78
00:03:35,449 --> 00:03:38,760
The chairman of Harvard’s Chemistry Department
Charles Lieber

79
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:41,590
was arrested on charges of lying about

80
00:03:41,590 --> 00:03:44,549
getting millions of dollars in Chinese funding.

81
00:03:44,549 --> 00:03:47,439
He’s a pioneer in the field of nanotechnology.

82
00:03:47,439 --> 00:03:49,699
That’s something the Chinese Communist Party

83
00:03:49,699 --> 00:03:52,449
