84
00:03:52,449 --> 00:03:55,809
And I know about mostly through Metal Gear.

85
00:03:55,809 --> 00:04:00,379
The nanomachines inside soldiers bodies adapt
to different conditions,

86
00:04:00,379 --> 00:04:03,939
promoting the release of neurotransmitters,
hormones, and stimulants,

87
00:04:03,939 --> 00:04:06,099
giving them an edge in battle.

88
00:04:06,099 --> 00:04:10,150
The US was funding Lieber’s research with
$15 million dollars.

89
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:11,659
At the same time,

90
00:04:11,659 --> 00:04:15,719
