Plan.

91
00:04:15,719 --> 00:04:16,719
As part of that,

92
00:04:16,719 --> 00:04:21,340
a Chinese tech university gave him $1.5 million
dollars

93
00:04:21,340 --> 00:04:23,530
to set up a research lab in China.

94
00:04:23,530 --> 00:04:29,190
“The school also agreed to pay him a $50,000
monthly salary

95
00:04:29,190 --> 00:04:33,030
and offered about $150,000 in annual living
expenses

96
00:04:33,030 --> 00:04:38,060
for “significant periods” from 2012 to
2017.”

97
00:04:38,060 --> 00:04:43,430
As a side note, that Chinese tech university
was located in Wuhan.

98
00:04:43,430 --> 00:04:47,040
So lucky for him, now that he’s been arrested
in the US,

99
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:49,280
